ABSTRACT
The Smart File Automation System is a Python-based application developed to automate file management operations. The project demonstrates file handling, CSV processing, activity logging, exception handling, and modular programming concepts.

OBJECTIVES
• Understand Python file handling.
• Implement file automation operations.
• Work with CSV files.
• Apply exception handling.
• Maintain activity logs.

FEATURES IMPLEMENTED
1. Create File
2. Read File
3. Write File
4. Rename File
5. Move File
6. Delete File
7. Read CSV File
8. Activity Logging

TECHNOLOGIES USED
• Python
• OS Module
• SHUTIL Module
• CSV Module
• Datetime Module
• Visual Studio Code

