RESULTS
The Smart File Automation System was successfully tested for all implemented functionalities. The application correctly performed file creation, reading, writing, renaming, moving, deletion, CSV file processing, and activity logging. All operations were executed successfully with proper exception handling.


CONCLUSION
The Smart File Automation System successfully automates common file management operations using Python. The project enhanced practical understanding of file handling, modular programming, exception handling, and logging mechanisms.
